&lt;li&gt;In MacOS, or Ubuntu  ifconfig -a&lt;br&gt;
Laptop has several network adapters, e.g., Ethernet and Wi-Fi. Thus, it will have several MAC addresses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
